"ຍັງເຫຼືອແຖວທີ່ບໍ່ຊໍ້າກັນ %s ແຖວ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"%s is not a valid day of month (it should be a number between 1 and 31)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນວັນທີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 1 ຫາ 31)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid day of week (it should be a number between 1 and 7)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນວັນໃນອາທິດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 1 ຫາ 7)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid hour (it should be a number between 0 and 23)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນຊົ່ວໂມງທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ 23)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid minute (it should be a number between 0 and 59)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນນາທີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ 59)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid month (it should be a number between 1 and 12)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນເດືອນທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 1 ຫາ 12)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid quarter (it should be a number between 1 and 4)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນໄຕມາດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 1 ຫາ 4)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid second (it should be a number between 0 and 59)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນວິນາທີທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ 59)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s is not a valid week (it should be a number between 0 and 53)"
msgstr "%s ບໍ່ແມ່ນອາທິດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ (ຄວນເປັນຕົວເລກລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ 53)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "%s matches in all sheets"
msgstr "ພົບ %s ລາຍການ ໃນທຸກແຜ່ນງານ"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"(0) Exact match.         (-1) Return next smaller item if no match.         "
"(1) Return next greater item if no match.         (2) Wildcard match."
msgstr ""
"(0) ກົງກັນແທ້. (-1) ສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການທີ່ນ້ອຍກວ່າຖ້າບໍ່ພົບ. (1) ສົ່ງຄືນລາຍການທີ່ໃຫຍ່ກວ່າຖ້າບໍ່ພົບ. (2) ໃຊ້ "
"Wildcard."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"(1) Search starting at first item.       (-1) Search starting at last item."
"       (2) Perform a binary search that relies on lookup_array being sorted "
"in ascending order. If not sorted, invalid results will be returned.       "
"(-2) Perform a binary search that relies on lookup_array being sorted in "
"descending order. If not sorted, invalid results will be returned.      "
msgstr ""
"(1) ຄົ້ນຫາໂດຍເລີ່ມຈາກລາຍການທຳອິດ       (-1) ຄົ້ນຫາໂດຍເລີ່ມຈາກລາຍການສຸດທ້າຍ       (2) ດໍາເ"
"ນີນການຄົ້ນຫາແບບໄບນາຣີ ໂດຍອີງຕາມ lookup_array ທີ່ໄດ້ຈັດລຽງຕາມລໍາດັບແຕ່ໜ້ອຍຫາຫຼາຍ. ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ຈັດລຽ"
"ງ, ຜົນລັດທີ່ສົ່ງກັບມາຈະບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ       (-2) ດໍາເນີນການຄົ້ນຫາແບບໄບນາຣີ ໂດຍອີງຕາມ lookup_array "
"ທີ່ໄດ້ຈັດລຽງຕາມລໍາດັບແຕ່ຫຼາຍຫາໜ້ອຍ. ຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ຈັດລຽງ, ຜົນລັດທີ່ສົ່ງກັບມາຈະບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ.      "

