#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given a general exponential form of y = b*m^x for a curve fit, calculates b "
"if TRUE or forces b to be 1 and only calculates the m values if FALSE."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດຮູບແບບເລກກຳລັງທົ່ວໄປຂອງ y = b*m^x ສຳລັບການປັບເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ, ຄິດໄລ່ b ຖ້າເປັນ TRUE ຫຼື ບັງຄັບໃ"
"ຫ້ b ເປັນ 1 ແລະ ຄິດໄລ່ສະເພາະຄ່າ m ຖ້າເປັນ FALSE."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given a general linear form of y = m*x+b for a curve fit, calculates b if "
"TRUE or forces b to be 0 and only calculates the m values if FALSE, i.e. "
"forces the curve fit to pass through the origin."
msgstr ""
"ກຳນົດຮູບແບບເສັ້ນຊື່ທົ່ວໄປຂອງ y = m*x+b ສຳລັບການປັບເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງ, ຄິດໄລ່ b ຖ້າເປັນ TRUE ຫຼື ບັງຄັບໃຫ້ b "
"ເປັນ 0 ແລະ ຄິດໄລ່ສະເພາະຄ່າ m ຖ້າເປັນ FALSE, ນັ້ນຄື ບັງຄັບໃຫ້ເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງຜ່ານຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ (0,0)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given partial data about a linear trend, calculates various parameters about"
" the ideal linear trend using the least-squares method."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກຂໍ້ມູນບາງສ່ວນກ່ຽວກັບແນວໂນ້ມເສັ້ນຊື່, ຄິດໄລ່ພາຣາມີເຕີຕ່າງໆກ່ຽວກັບແນວໂນ້ມເສັ້ນຊື່ທີ່ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດ ໂດຍໃຊ້ວິທີ"
"ກຳລັງສອງໜ້ອຍສຸດ (Least-squares method)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Given partial data about an exponential growth curve, calculates various "
"parameters about the best fit ideal exponential growth curve."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກຂໍ້ມູນບາງສ່ວນກ່ຽວກັບເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງການເຕີບໂຕແບບເລກກຳລັງ, ຄິດໄລ່ພາຣາມີເຕີຕ່າງໆກ່ຽວກັບເສັ້ນໂຄ້ງການເຕີບໂຕ"
"ແບບເລກກຳລັງທີ່ເໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດ."

